import React, { useEffect } from 'react' // import Custom Components import Header from '../../containers/common/header' import BannerSection from '../layouts/sections/modern-sass/banner' import FeatureSection from '../layouts/sections/modern-sass/feature' import BuildSection from '../layouts/sections/modern-sass/build' import WorkSection from '../layouts/sections/modern-sass/work' import PriceSection from '../layouts/sections/modern-sass/price' import FaqSection from '../layouts/sections/modern-sass/faq' import CtaSection from '../layouts/sections/modern-sass/cta' import ClientSection from '../layouts/sections/modern-sass/client' const ModernSass = () => { useEffect(() => { document.body.style.setProperty('--primary', '#fb3b64') document.body.style.setProperty('--secondary', '#071828') document.body.style.setProperty('--light', '#071828') document.body.style.setProperty('--dark', '#fb3b64') }) return (
) } export default ModernSass;
